      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Développer en série de Fourier la fonction : $x  \\mapsto |\\sin x|$.",
        "html": "<p>Développer en série de Fourier la fonction : <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x  \\mapsto |\\sin x|\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "99e64719-03bb-41fb-b712-02c2671fb6bb",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Application : Soit $f : {[a,b]} \\to \\R$ continue.\n    Montrer que $ \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)|\\sin nt|\\,d t \\to\n    \\frac2\\pi \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)\\,d t$ lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p>Application : Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : {[a,b]} \\to\n\\R\\)</span> continue. Montrer que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\int_{t=a}^b f(t)|\\sin nt|\\,d t \\to\n    \\frac2\\pi \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)\\,d t\\)</span> lorsque <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b1cdf888-69ce-4c79-ac7f-b900fd174be2",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$|\\sin x| = \\frac2\\pi -\\frac 4\\pi\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty\n             \\frac{\\cos 2nx}{4n^2-1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(|\\sin x| = \\frac2\\pi -\\frac\n4\\pi\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty\n             \\frac{\\cos 2nx}{4n^2-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
